Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.98,0:02:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这就是以第二代白濑号为基础
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.16,0:02:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}改造成的新南极观测船–七神屋企鹅馒头号
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.88,0:02:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}基础性能维持了原样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.91,0:02:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但船内进行了一些改良
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.12,0:02:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}外观也变成看到的这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.98,0:03:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就让我们赶快进去—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.81,0:03:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}虽然很想这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.24,0:03:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过我们得到澳大利亚才搭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.90,0:03:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以就让我们一口气跳到澳洲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.42,0:03:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}1 2
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.61,0:03:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Jumping！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.58,0:03:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}OK
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.60,0:03:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不愧是专业的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.64,0:03:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好强喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.52,0:03:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们在开我玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.73,0:03:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}才没有啦 我们很尊敬你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.83,0:03:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们看 下次报告要等到了澳洲才做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.10,0:03:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但那边已经变成这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.70,0:03:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我…我现在在澳大利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.46,0:03:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不对 得先跳一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.88,0:03:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}着地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.75,0:03:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不对 先着地再跳才对？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.74,0:03:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}着地 着地是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.32,0:03:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}报濑 你冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.00,0:03:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么办 我没办法在澳大利亚着地啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.82,0:03:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那会用剪辑处理好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.49,0:03:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你得先做发音练习
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.37,0:03:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你有做发音练习吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.07,0:03:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}红红水黾因为爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.87,0:03:55.99,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}※原本是日语假名识字歌「あめんぼあかいなあいうえお（红红水黾红又圆）」。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.94,0:03:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}错了一点点 不过不计较了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.61,0:04:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么水黾是红的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.38,0:04:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}请你别纠结识字歌了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.02,0:04:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么会变成这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.03,0:04:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}朝会时说得挺有气势的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.32,0:04:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为这里没有她的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.56,0:04:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果周围有「敌人」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.32,0:04:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她马上就会像「搞毛啊」这样被打开开关了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.53,0:04:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.78,0:04:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那边的 你们刚刚说我坏话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.61,0:04:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的要搭上这艘船啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.67,0:04:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.50,0:04:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}收拾好行李了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.03,0:04:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.97,0:04:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还挺犹豫的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.69,0:04:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.67,0:04:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}算上自己的体重 最多能带100公斤上船吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.93,0:04:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有这么多就够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.61,0:04:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我们要在那边待上三个多月吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.30,0:04:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对 要带90套以上换洗衣物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.55,0:04:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}请你洗衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.00,0:04:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.28,0:04:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}说是旅行 到了那边还是正常过日子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.05,0:04:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且据说工作很多 会觉得时间过得很快
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.27,0:04:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过一边思考一边往纸箱里塞东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.78,0:05:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知不觉就会塞很多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.96,0:05:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}会这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.45,0:05:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不会还完全没开始准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但算上体重不超过100公斤就好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.67,0:05:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我可以带52 53…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.70,0:05:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可以带58公斤的行李呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.52,0:05:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}轻轻松松啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.23,0:05:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谎报体重可是重罪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.18,0:05:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}58公斤的行李 就是说你42公斤重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.53,0:05:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}放开我的上臂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.25,0:05:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可能是有点难带上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.13,0:05:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真理 不是跟你说自己的换洗衣物自己带…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.87,0:05:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真理？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.13,0:05:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.04,0:05:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你用不到厨具吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.75,0:05:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.02,0:06:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这可是金刚石涂层 绝对不黏的锅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.99,0:06:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.71,0:06:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}救生圈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.05,0:06:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.60,0:06:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}英日词典
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.97,0:06:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}日英词典、《旅行英文会话》、削皮器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.84,0:06:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}《旅行中文会话》、《帮您安心走世界》
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.53,0:06:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我好不容易买的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.48,0:06:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你会碰上很多会说外语的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.49,0:06:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是这样没错啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.06,0:06:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大概就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.57,0:06:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好少
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.71,0:06:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你再问问报濑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.06,0:06:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}肯定有些东西是必带的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.38,0:06:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但这么点真的够吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.85,0:06:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要待上三个多月呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.49,0:06:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}姐姐 你真的没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.53,0:06:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为那本宣传册没写要带什么东西去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.92,0:06:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为那里都是大人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.21,0:06:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要对自己负责的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.81,0:06:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对自己负责…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.04,0:06:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}当个大人真不容易
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.77,0:06:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.04,0:07:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.03,0:07:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其实是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.94,0:07:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你看！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.70,0:07:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.53,0:07:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是小惠的游戏 我还以为弄丢了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.96,0:07:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是有这回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.97,0:07:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没必要再开机检查了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.99,0:07:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为隔了这么久 它才冒出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.49,0:07:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都快三年了 说不定已经开不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.11,0:07:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好怀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.57,0:07:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你那时很喜欢这游戏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.84,0:07:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 因为这是我唯一赢过你的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.13,0:07:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.35,0:07:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为小惠你完全打不过我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.43,0:07:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以才愿意无限期地借给我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.57,0:07:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.61,0:07:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你就弄丢了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.63,0:07:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}结果上是这样没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.38,0:07:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但弄丢之前 我一直都赢你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.39,0:07:58.18,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\fn华康勘亭流\bord5\fs50\1c&HEFF6F7&\3c&H666695&\t(300,600,0\fs65)\t(600,900,0\fs50)\t(900,1200,0\fs65)\t(1200,1500,0\fs50)\t(1500,1800,0\fs65)\t(1800,2100,0\fs50)\t(2100,2400,0\fs65)\t(2400,2700,0\fs50)\pos(302,92)}耶！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.26,0:07:58.18,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\jitter(0,-5,2,10,200)\fad(300,0)\fn华康勘亭流\bord5\fs50\1c&H5B5164&\3c&HD6DBDF&\pos(872,8)}输了～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.56,0:07:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我赢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.78,0:08:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}去东京的事呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.28,0:08:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 基本上挺顺利的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}南极她能做好报导的工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.37,0:08:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}南极？你说报濑？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.98,0:08:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还没轮到她出场呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.69,0:08:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那家伙也够怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.74,0:08:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.94,0:08:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我和日向也聊过 不知道她到底坚强还是软弱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.20,0:08:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和你一起打工的那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.50,0:08:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 不过结月能把报导的事完美解决
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.00,0:08:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}北海道的那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.56,0:08:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.93,0:08:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别累坏自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.02,0:08:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是没成功 你会很懊悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.13,0:08:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.78,0:08:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.27,0:09:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.72,0:09:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.83,0:09:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}南极挑战…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.44,0:09:20.05,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康俪中黑\bord0.5\shad2\fs30\1vc(&H84906C&,&H8B9C85&,&H92A596&,&H9FB4B8&)\4c&H716654&\move(568,90,814,252,34,660)\frz348.8}比宇宙更遥远的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.44,0:09:20.05,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fn华康俪中黑\bord0\shad2\fs20\1vc(&H84906C&,&H8B9C85&,&H92A596&,&H9FB4B8&)\4c&H716654&\frz346.7\frx358\fry6\move(554,286,794,452,34,660)}小渊泽贵子
