Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.79,0:09:39.11,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,0)\fn华康粗圆体\bord0\1c&H929588&\fs50\be1\frz15.57\pos(482,456)}爱菜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.11,0:09:40.36,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康中特圆体\bord0\1c&H836ECA&\fs80\be1\frz358.9\frx350\fry18\pos(592,444)}删除
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.81,0:09:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.51,0:09:57.05,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康中特圆体\bord0\1c&H9A7DCA&\frz349.8\frx336\fry348\pos(4,122)}收件人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.51,0:09:57.05,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康中特圆体\bord0\b0\fs80\1c&H535F5D&\rnd20\frz349.8\frx358\fry354\pos(460,146)}南极挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.99,0:10:05.80,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,0)\fs80\1c&H5D7B5D&\bord4\3c&H948B96&\move(422,-66,446,0,0,864)}南{\3c&H4F9D5B&}极{\3c&H417B62&}一{\3c&H4E5D3E&}路{\3c&H6B6260&}顺{\3c&H5CA28A&}风{\3c&H39743D&}！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.99,0:10:05.80,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,0)\fs80\1c&H5D7B5D&\3c&H2D573D&\move(422,-66,446,0,0,864)}南极一路顺风！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.62,0:10:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.40,0:10:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}带块浮冰回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.35,0:10:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还不知道能不能带呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.94,0:10:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我会发你些暖洋洋的照片的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.95,0:10:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.20,0:10:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在南极是不是鼻涕都会结冰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.89,0:10:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好想吃刨冰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.42,0:10:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}南极真的埋着UFO吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.09,0:10:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感觉就像要转学了一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.37,0:10:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再见 摇摇布丁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.22,0:10:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}得暂时跟你告别了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.18,0:10:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也没有别的送行方法了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.99,0:10:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我没想到会用这么大排场嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.98,0:10:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}报濑说要去南极的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.63,0:10:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大家还当他笨蛋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.35,0:10:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都觉得是天方夜谭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.39,0:10:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且现在还是有人当他笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.19,0:10:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.73,0:10:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这里也有三个多月没来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.82,0:11:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}寂寞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.07,0:11:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是 只是不知道自己会是什么心情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.70,0:11:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不要太招摇比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.70,0:11:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有不少人嫌你们得意忘形呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.17,0:11:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没什么好招摇的吧 明天就要出发啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.17,0:11:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}话是这么说啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.83,0:11:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是谣言传得很凶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.70,0:11:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.07,0:11:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大概是嫉妒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.04,0:11:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}说你们为了筹钱去便利商店行窃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.13,0:11:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}经常去歌舞伎町陪男人鬼混…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.65,0:11:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是怎样！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.99,0:11:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是说 有人认为你们太跩了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.23,0:11:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}才没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.92,0:11:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.01,0:11:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.56,0:11:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样出发真的没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.50,0:11:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}回来后 说不定情况会更糟糕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.15,0:11:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.70,0:11:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}难道说这个人就是小惠？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.99,0:12:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊 日向还是第一次见到她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.83,0:12:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是和小理一起打工的三宅日向 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.95,0:12:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.87,0:12:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.01,0:12:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.05,0:12:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.17,0:12:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你刚才说的那些
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.93,0:12:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是谁在那边乱说的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.06,0:12:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也只是听说而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.28,0:12:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}绝对要把犯人抓出来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.79,0:12:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}报濑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.69,0:12:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明天就要出发了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.23,0:12:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样胡说八道 怎么能忍气吞声呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.20,0:12:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}现在把事情闹大也无济于事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.47,0:12:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们一直都对风言风语不理不睬的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.56,0:12:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}继续无视就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.73,0:12:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这可不一样 这些都是假话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.51,0:12:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们哪有去新宿跟男人鬼混
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.88,0:12:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}事实就是去过新宿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.61,0:12:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}才没有鬼混
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.01,0:12:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你能证明吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.01,0:12:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样太奇怪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.56,0:12:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小惠 你怎么看？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.29,0:12:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你问我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.71,0:12:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}每个人都有恶毒的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.03,0:12:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要以恶报恶 挺起胸膛做人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.20,0:12:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}名言？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.15,0:13:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那当然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.63,0:13:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且现在在这里的也不止你一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.42,0:13:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么说？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.89,0:13:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你有能倾吐不满的对象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.72,0:13:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.43,0:13:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是这个味
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原来下班途中喝一杯 就是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.97,0:13:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也不是不能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.77,0:13:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好咧 再来一罐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.65,0:13:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天发薪水 我请你们喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.93,0:13:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我还是很不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.82,0:13:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你真是记仇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.72,0:13:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是错肯定在传谣言的人身上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.70,0:13:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}凭什么我要…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.60,0:13:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我懂我懂 请用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.62,0:13:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好想尽情大吼发泄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.30,0:13:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就吼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.87,0:13:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在寺庙后大吼大叫不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.74,0:13:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就去卡拉OK
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.92,0:13:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还有一个小时 应该没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.72,0:13:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我还没去过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.04,0:13:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.67,0:13:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.73,0:13:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.72,0:13:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么大家敢做那么丢人的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.09,0:14:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大声吼出来就行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.22,0:14:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就当是饯别会啦 饯别会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.80,0:14:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.28,0:14:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.25,0:14:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小惠也要去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.08,0:14:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.65,0:14:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一起去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}气氛嗨起来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.05,0:14:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小渊泽报濑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.55,0:14:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.78,0:14:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.18,0:14:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就高桥惠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.09,0:14:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的好友小惠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.75,0:14:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}气氛嗨起来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.52,0:14:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小渊泽报濑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.67,0:14:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小渊泽报濑 小渊泽报濑 小渊泽报濑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.52,0:14:46.99,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn@华康布丁体W7\bord0\fs65\frz274\frx338\fry4\1c&H6370CB&\be2\rnd8\move(1150,22,1144,402,0,658)}报{\1c&H64D8BD&}濑{\1c&HCED9AA&}疯{\1c&H3DDFEB&}了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.99,0:14:50.54,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn@华康布丁体W7\bord0\fs65\frz274\frx338\fry4\1c&H6370CB&\be2\rnd8\move(1144,402,1142,62,0,2566)}报{\1c&H64D8BD&}濑{\1c&HCED9AA&}疯{\1c&H3DDFEB&}了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.31,0:14:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还好没跟她们一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.58,0:14:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.26,0:14:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.09,0:15:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 最棒的一晚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.53,0:15:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没想到出发前一天还能来这么一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.83,0:15:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你想 自从决定去南极之后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.31,0:15:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就没什么机会和你一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.04,0:15:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}虽然小惠你好像不在意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.45,0:15:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那种事…算了 其实我也是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.45,0:15:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.59,0:15:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是我心里很在意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.44,0:15:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我一直都在想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.84,0:15:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想去遥远的地方啦 不想待在这里啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.97,0:15:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}讨厌自己之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.82,0:15:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我为什么会有这些想法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.11,0:15:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大概是因为小惠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.20,0:15:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我总是慢吞吞的 一直要小惠照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.66,0:15:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}老是黏着你问东问西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.39,0:15:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有这回事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.61,0:15:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.55,0:15:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我讨厌这点 所以一直想改变吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.54,0:15:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不想黏在你身边 不想当你口中的废柴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.44,0:15:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}至少想成为你游戏的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.09,0:16:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.84,0:16:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.89,0:16:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.94,0:16:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是怎样 好丰盛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.82,0:16:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这么晚才回来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.90,0:16:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就当送行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.18,0:16:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.97,0:16:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可不止那些喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.85,0:16:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}来啦 鸡蛋天国
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.37,0:16:34.90,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康俪中黑\bord0\fs20\1c&HB0A993&\frz4.023\pos(548,32)}小理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.37,0:16:34.90,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康俪中黑\bord0\fs20\1c&H6A6B6A&\frz3.948\be1\pos(484,174)}来吃吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.56,0:17:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.27,0:17:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.98,0:17:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我走了 我走了 我走了 我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.33,0:17:16.87,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)\fnGen Jyuu Gothic Heavy\fs80\xshad-5\1c&H4856A6&\3c&H354060&\4c&H3D4664&\frz2.458\frx348\fry0\pos(512,192)}在房间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.13,0:17:20.86,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\fnGen Jyuu Gothic Heavy\fs80\xshad-5\1c&HAD8769&\3c&H354060&\4c&H756048&\frz2.458\pos(512,192)\frx334\fry358}出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.20,0:17:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.32,0:17:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要出发了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.14,0:17:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.16,0:17:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要在东京吃早餐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.20,0:17:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.38,0:17:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.78,0:17:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}铃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.48,0:17:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么不叫醒我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.34,0:17:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.96,0:17:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我好担心你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.56,0:17:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我会加油不让你担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.55,0:17:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.19,0:18:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小惠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.86,0:18:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不好意思 出发日早上来见你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.10,0:18:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.51,0:18:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我来和你绝交
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.10,0:18:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我说和你绝交
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.34,0:18:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么了 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.51,0:18:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我说你 还没注意到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.58,0:18:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你和南极去新宿的事 为什么传开来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.46,0:18:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你和别人说过吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.31,0:18:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.73,0:18:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你最初遇上南极时 为什么高年级的知道她有100万？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.55,0:18:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么你还没开口 你妈就知道你要去南极了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.67,0:18:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.36,0:18:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}除了我还能是谁啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.56,0:18:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还以为你很快会发现 然后大发脾气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.57,0:18:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是真这么以为的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.83,0:18:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只是时间上的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.13,0:19:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.13,0:19:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是你跟南极她们都像个笨蛋一样没发现
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.15,0:19:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.00,0:19:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谁知道啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.11,0:19:16.79,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}そっと「会いたい」闻いた
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.41,0:19:25.23,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}空に溶けて消えた
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.10,0:19:42.81,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}今も胸の奥　静かに揺れている
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.81,0:19:50.60,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}白く辉く世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.28,0:19:58.94,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}残した足迹も消えて
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.76,0:20:07.02,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}果てないと思ってた时が
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.47,0:20:15.40,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}终わりを告げる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.52,0:20:25.23,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}だからずっと忘れない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.37,0:20:34.68,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}言叶より大切な思いが
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.68,0:20:43.97,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}きっと繋いでくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.62,0:20:55.88,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}いつの日か　また旅に出よう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.73,0:21:07.41,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}だからずっと忘れない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.41,0:21:17.04,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}一绪にいた　かけがえのない时が
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.04,0:21:26.25,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}きっと繋いでくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.98,0:21:37.97,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}いつまでも　いつまでも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.44,0:21:43.22,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}またね
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.11,0:19:16.79,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}听见一声轻轻的「想见你」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.41,0:19:25.23,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}声音渐渐消失在了空中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.10,0:19:42.81,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}我的心底依然在暗自动摇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.81,0:19:50.60,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}雪白闪耀的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.28,0:19:58.94,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}我们踩下的足迹 渐渐褪去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.76,0:20:07.02,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}原以为这些时光 永无止境
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.47,0:20:15.40,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}却突然画上了句号
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.52,0:20:25.23,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}所以这份心情 我不会忘怀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.37,0:20:34.68,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}它比任何语言 都要宝贵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.68,0:20:43.97,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}总有一天 会再度牵起你我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.62,0:20:55.88,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}带着我们 又一次踏上旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.73,0:21:07.41,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}所以这些时光 我不会忘怀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.41,0:21:17.04,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}你我一道 度过的珍贵点滴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.04,0:21:26.25,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}想必它们 会永远牵起你我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.98,0:21:37.97,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}直到永远 直到永恒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.44,0:21:43.22,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.54,0:19:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你一开始跟我说要去南极的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.60,0:19:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就在想为什么我会这么生气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.17,0:19:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小理以前不管做什么都会先找我商量的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.77,0:19:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}骗人的吧 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.30,0:19:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉让你留下不好的回忆 我道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.70,0:19:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.44,0:19:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}昨天听你一说 我才发现
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.72,0:19:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一直黏着人的不是你 是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.76,0:19:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你会依靠我 会找我商量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.98,0:19:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就会装出一副 拿你没辙只好帮帮你的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.95,0:19:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}总是什么都明白似的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.69,0:19:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为不这么做 我就一无所有了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.26,0:20:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为自己一无所有 所以想让你也一无所有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.47,0:20:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}废柴的不是你 是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.19,0:20:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}必须走出这个小世界的 是我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.41,0:20:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再见…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.29,0:20:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小惠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.04,0:20:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一起去吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.29,0:20:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.88,0:20:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}南极
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.88,0:20:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}说什么傻话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.82,0:20:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我终于打算向 没有你的世界前进了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.89,0:21:04.19,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)\fn华康粗圆体\bord0\fs30\1c&H4D453F&\pos(452,290)\frz25.47\frx350\fry358}新讯息
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.89,0:21:04.19,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)\fn华康粗圆体\bord0\fs45\1c&H9D9A92&\pos(484,350)\frz26.57\frx340\fry352}收件者：{\1c&H4D453F&}母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.89,0:21:04.19,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)\fn华康粗圆体\bord0\fs45\1c&H9D9A92&\frx340\fry352\pos(616,528)\frz27.7}主旨：{\1c&H565350&}致母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.01,0:21:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们会向新世界踏出脚步
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.92,0:21:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在那片世界 没有我们依靠过的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.84,0:21:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在那片世界 我们前途未卜 也不知家在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.63,0:21:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在那片世界 我们想象不到明天会身在何处
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.84,0:21:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}更想象不到后天会去往何方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.54,0:21:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我们依然会踏出脚步
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.75,0:21:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}绝交无效！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.63,0:21:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我喜欢等水积满沙槽 看水倾泻而出的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.98,0:21:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大水决堤 得以解放 奔流而下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.19,0:21:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沙槽里蓄满的能量爆发开
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.96,0:21:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一切都会动起来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.06,0:22:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一切都会动起来！
Comment: 0,0:22:03.04,0:22:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,ED-FF FINAL
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.20,0:22:23.89,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}长いトンネルの出口を探していた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.27,0:22:34.81,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}かすかな光の匂いがしてる方へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.18,0:22:40.43,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}间违っても　笑えるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.43,0:22:51.38,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}ここから始めよう　仆は旅に出よう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.59,0:23:02.13,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}污れた真ん丸のビー玉　握りしめて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.29,0:23:13.40,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}言えなかった言叶も　きっと见つかるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.56,0:23:19.02,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}バカにされたって构わない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.02,0:23:24.35,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}信じてゆこう
